All Implemented Interfaces:

public class AccountsGUI
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.WindowListener

Used as the main class which builds the Account Records GUI the AccountsGUIButtonManager and the AccountsGUIListener classes are also used for the purpose of expanding this class using association in which is where most of the complex work is done
